						</div>
						<div class="mt-4 rounded-xl border border-border bg-muted/20 p-5">
							<p class="font-bold text-foreground text-xs mb-3">Example B: Sofia, 28, 58 kg, 19% body fat, beginner lifter (4 months)</p>
							<div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3 text-xs">
